    <note>Guo(1) Zhongjian [26324] Bi Zhongyou, WJ, 14.13a-15a (wife, born Tian(1), who married him at age 16 and died in 1113 at age 58). Tian(1) Ruren was only 27 years old when he died and her parents urged her to remarry, but she protected principle and remained a chaste widow. Zhongjian's father identified as Kui [8072] on basis of zi Zhongtong. Not indexed in CBD.</note>
